headline: Ford Stock Is Trading Below $10: Should You Buy It Hand Over Fist Right Now and Hold for 20 Years?
summary: While monster technology enterprises draw all the attention, it's worth pointing out that Ford Motor Company (NYSE: F) was once considered the bellwether of the American economy.  While traditional mass-market automakers don't typically trade at high multiples, some investors may view Ford's current setup as a fat pitch.  Another reason to be bullish on the business is the success of Ford Pro.
